in the direction

15:09.103 --> 15:11.310
of a boat named "The Blue"?

15:11.379 --> 15:14.689
They all look the same to me.

15:14.758 --> 15:15.689
Yeah.

15:15.758 --> 15:17.551
Yeah, I-- I guess I know her.

15:38.793 --> 15:40.689
The skipper doesn't
like the marina crowd,

15:40.758 --> 15:44.068
so he usually moors
further out

15:44.137 --> 15:46.827
away from the wankers.

16:19.896 --> 16:23.275
Michelle!

16:23.344 --> 16:25.655
You've got visitors.

16:25.724 --> 16:30.137
Are you Michelle Wilson?

16:30.206 --> 16:34.482
We found this on the
street in the old town.

16:34.551 --> 16:37.827
We were gonna hand
it to the police,

16:37.896 --> 16:40.068
but we found this
old ticket thing.

16:40.137 --> 16:45.241
So we figured if we found the
boat on the ticket, then yeah.

16:45.310 --> 16:47.172
Fuck.
Thank you.

16:47.241 --> 16:48.413
Thanks.

16:48.482 --> 16:49.517
The money's gone.

16:49.586 --> 16:51.137
Jesus, who cares?

16:51.206 --> 16:52.413
I mean, they brought it back.

16:52.482 --> 16:53.724
That's all that matters.

16:53.793 --> 16:54.517
Thanks.

16:54.586 --> 16:56.172
It's all good.

16:56.241 --> 16:59.448
Yeah, so this is Kitty.

16:59.517 --> 17:01.517
