17:17.172 --> 17:19.137
Stroke of luck.

17:19.206 --> 17:20.586
Yeah.

17:20.655 --> 17:22.965
Well, we know what it's
like to get robbed.

17:24.517 --> 17:26.206
Don't we, Lana?

17:26.275 --> 17:28.931
